<i>Decisions I made
Thought I was a thug</i>

21:10.020 --> 21:12.731
<i>Dropped outta school and smoked
stuff that's like a drug</i>

21:12.814 --> 21:15.567
<i>A broke-down filthy
homeless substance abuser</i>

21:15.650 --> 21:18.653
<i>And now I'm richer
than all y'all losers</i>

21:18.737 --> 21:21.531
<i>Now he's richer
than all y'all ugly losers</i>

